Type Parameters:
DTO - The Data Transfer Object type, extending SuperDto. This represents the data structure used for transferring data between the client and the server.
S - The Service type, extending SuperService. This provides CRUD operations for entities. It provides default implementations for saving, retrieving, updating, and deleting entities using a corresponding SuperService.

This class is designed to be extended by concrete REST controllers, which should specify the DTO type and the service type.

DTO - The Data Transfer Object type, extending SuperDto. This represents the data structure used for transferring data between the client and the server.
S - The Service type, extending SuperService. This provides the business logic for the entity.
Direct Known Subclasses:
AuthorRestController, AvisRestController, CategoryRestController, GameRestController, InventoryRestController, PublisherRestController, PurchaseLineRestController, PurchaseRestController, UserRestController, WishlistRestController
public abstract class SuperRestController<DTO extends SuperDto,S extends SuperService<?,DTO,? extends SuperRepository<?>,? extends SuperMapper<DTO,?>>> extends Object
This class is an abstract base class for REST controllers that handle common CRUD operations for entities. It provides default implementations for saving, retrieving, updating, and deleting entities using a corresponding SuperService.

This class is designed to be extended by concrete REST controllers, which should specify the DTO type and the service type.
